lineString.description: An array of two or more positions

linearRing.description: An array of four positions where the first equals the last

route.description: Route of a line consisting of a stopsequence and days of service

parts.description: details per one (or more) sub-part of part

coupledTrips.description: (at least one) all trips that run together on this part

position.description: Position of this trip within the couple of trips, starting with 1 (0 means unknown). Position is valid for stop where passenger boards (when used in trip request context)

positionOverall.description: Sequential number of this vehicle over all CoupledTrips (1 = first vehicle in front)

positionInCoupledTrip.description: Sequential number of this vehicle within the CoupledTrip (1 = first vehicle in front)

stopEventType.description: applies for departure, arrival or both

continuousVehicles.description: List of vehicles where boarding at origin of requested part and alighting at this stop is possible

start.description: Start of vehicle position (in millimeters in relation to a reference point at the platform)

end.description: End of vehicle position (in millimeters in relation to a reference point at the platform)
